      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALMIGHTY RUSH (6) finished 7 metres from the winner in third at this track over 2190m last start at her first career run. Her debut form is good enough to take out a race like this. ROYAL ROCKSTAR (7) settled handy and finished well but could only manage second last start over 1790m here, that effort coming on the back of a sound third at Horsham the run before. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. Won't find this any harder and he can find winning ways. LISTEN TO THE HAND (5) last appeared when sixth over 1650m at Bendigo 11 months ago. Look out for any positive market movement. SWEET LUCY LOU (9) could only finish sixth over 2190m at this course most recently. Open to improvement and is in the mix for some minor money.",
